###  http://example.org/data/CharlesChaplin
<http://example.org/data/CharlesChaplin> rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                                                  <https://schema.org/Person> ;
                                         <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/race> "White" ;
                                         <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/religion> "Atheist" ;
                                         <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/sexualOrientation> "Straight" ;
                                         <https://schema.org/name> "Charles Chaplin" .


###  http://example.org/data/Nomination1
<http://example.org/data/Nomination1> rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
